FsF_F2_01M-1-2-3.creator: Di Tecco, Antonio
FsF_F2_01M-1-2-3.title: Dataset DT22
FsF_F2_01M-1-2-3.summary: Dataset is a collection of the emotional states of 112 participants involved in the experiment named Sperimentazione DT22. It was presented in part and cited in the following article and book: Di Tecco, A., Foglia, P., & Prete, C. A. (2024). Video Quality Prediction: An Exploratory Study with Valence and Arousal Signals. IEEE Access. DOI: 0.1109/ACCESS.2024.3374056. Di Tecco, A. (2024). Intelligent Systems for Human Health and Well-Being. The dataset is not currently available for distribution.
FsF_F2_01M-1-2-3.keywords: dataset dt22, database dt22, emotion, valence, arousal, dominance, quality, satisfaction, interest, involvement, Machine learning, Pattern recognition, Supervised learning, Unsupervised learning, Psychology, Psychiatry, Cognitive psychology, Economics and business

FsF_A1_01M-1.comment: The dataset is not currently available for distribution, but the creator is working to make it accessible as soon as possible. (source: Embedded Metadata)
